snippet.title: My World #31: Joining Russo's WCW
snippet.description:
On this episode of My World with Jeff Jarrett, Jeff and Conrad revisit the time Jeff left the WWF (again) for the sinking ship that is World Championship Wrestling, reuniting with Vince Russo! The guys discuss Jeff debuting on Monday Nitro and the guitar smash to Buff Bagwell, "The Chosen One" and "Slapnuts" origins, the WCW World Title Tournament, Jeff's opening match at Mayhem 1999 vs. Chris Benoit, and much more!
